284
00:17:56,000 --> 00:18:00,800
So, we only tell them everything is great.

285
00:18:02,000 --> 00:18:05,000
Minor problems don't have to be mentioned.

286
00:18:05,000 --> 00:18:09,200
Once, Dayang had a bad cold.

287
00:18:09,200 --> 00:18:13,000
It was so severe that he had to be hospitalized in the ICU.

288
00:18:13,000 --> 00:18:14,400
We had no clue.

289
00:18:14,400 --> 00:18:15,600
When it was the Lunar New Year,

290
00:18:15,600 --> 00:18:17,100
