291
00:18:17,100 --> 00:18:19,900
Xiao Xi spilled the beans.

292
00:18:21,030 --> 00:18:25,434
I was so furious that the New Year was ruined.

293
00:18:27,800 --> 00:18:29,300
Think about it.

294
00:18:30,400 --> 00:18:33,400
A cold can kill...

295
00:18:33,400 --> 00:18:35,300
or send someone to the ICU.

296
00:18:35,300 --> 00:18:38,200
