300
00:18:49,300 --> 00:18:52,700
You're so eloquent and logical

301
00:18:52,700 --> 00:18:54,400
when talking sense into others.

302
00:18:54,400 --> 00:18:59,000
Why are you so muddled about your own matters?

303
00:19:02,600 --> 00:19:06,300
Don't shoulder everything on your own.

304
00:19:06,300 --> 00:19:10,700
You need to communicate with your family, especially with your parents.

305
00:19:10,700 --> 00:19:12,600
