00:21:51,900 --> 00:21:53,200
It's hard, isn't it?

358
00:21:53,200 --> 00:21:54,200
Not really.

359
00:21:54,200 --> 00:21:55,800
When I think about how our acquaintances are starring in this,

360
00:21:55,800 --> 00:21:57,400
I get so inspired.

361
00:21:57,400 --> 00:22:00,000
I have to say, this is really entertaining.

362
00:22:00,000 --> 00:22:01,400
Right?

363
00:22:01,400 --> 00:22:02,800
When I watch television,

364
00:22:02,800 --> 00:22:03,600
I always think these scriptwriters are ridiculous.

365
00:22:03,600 --> 00:22:05,400
Even I can do the same!

366
00:22:05,400 --> 00:22:07,800
Well, is there anything you feel

367
00:22:07,800 --> 00:22:11,900
