I'm 100% satisfied with it so far.

369
00:22:14,300 --> 00:22:15,800
Let me put it this way.

370
00:22:15,800 --> 00:22:17,700
I think my writing is very coherent throughout.

371
00:22:17,700 --> 00:22:18,700
What do you think?

372
00:22:18,700 --> 00:22:20,600
I think...

373
00:22:20,600 --> 00:22:23,000
this isn't a script.

374
00:22:24,300 --> 00:22:25,800
You're right.

375
00:22:25,800 --> 00:22:29,700
I wrote this script like a novel.

376
00:22:29,700 --> 00:22:32,000
You think this is a novel?

377
00:22:33,000 --> 00:22:35,900
I know a novel needs a plot,

378
00:22:35,900 --> 00:22:38,400
but this is a promotional video.

379
00:22:38,400 --> 00:22:42,800
So, I deliberately added comic scenes to it.

380
00:22:42,800 --> 00:22:44,200
Comic scenes?

381
00:22:44,200 --> 00:22:46,500
For example?

382
00:22:46,500 --> 00:22:48,200
For example...

383
00:22:49,981 --> 00:22:51,590
Weren't you laughing your head off just now?

384
00:22:51,600 --> 00:22:53,800
Tell her what you were laughing at.

385
00:22:53,800 --> 00:22:55,600
Over here.

386
00:22:55,600 --> 00:22:58,900
Huang Xinxin was scared by a dog at the seaside.

387
00:22:58,900 --> 00:23:03,000
Xiao Hulu, Tuotuo, Huzi, and Guobao leaped in to protect her.

388
00:23:03,000 --> 00:23:05,500
The four children didn't defeat the dog.

389
00:23:05,500 --> 00:23:10,400
The five of them ran off crying while chased by the dog.

390
00:23:10,400 --> 00:23:14,800
This scene of running

391
00:23:14,800 --> 00:23:18,800
will spotlight our village's scenic seaside.

392
00:23:18,800 --> 00:23:20,800
There's this part as well.

393
00:23:24,400 --> 00:23:29,800
Xu Hongdou rides a bicycle while chortling away in Youfeng Courtyard.

394
00:23:29,800 --> 00:23:33,100
Na Na sprays water at her with the hose for watering flowers.

395
00:23:33,100 --> 00:23:35,400
Xu Hongdou dodges with a dainty smile,

396
00:23:35,400 --> 00:23:39,200
and the radiant sun shines upon a rainbow.

397
00:23:39,200 --> 00:23:41,800
Hongdou, this isn't a comic scene.

398
00:23:41,800 --> 00:23:45,400
This serves to highlight the supreme romance

399
00:23:45,400 --> 00:23:48,200
and friendship between people.

400
00:23:48,200 --> 00:23:51,000
The ending is the most hilarious.

401
00:23:51,000 --> 00:23:55,100
Xie Zhiyao grabbed a flag from the villagers.

402
00:23:55,100 --> 00:24:00,000
He rides his horse past the sea and mountains.

403
00:24:00,000 --> 00:24:03,800
At the highest point overlooking Yunmiao Village,

404
00:24:03,800 --> 00:24:07,900
he puts down the flag reading, "Welcome to Yunmiao Village."

405
00:24:07,900 --> 00:24:11,500
The audience doesn't know what he grabbed,

406
00:24:11,500 --> 00:24:14,200
so that triggers...

407
00:24:14,200 --> 00:24:15,600
a form of suspense.

408
00:24:15,600 --> 00:24:17,500
Suspense?

409
00:24:19,300 --> 00:24:22,000
It's way too comical.

410
00:24:22,000 --> 00:24:23,200
Hilarious!

411
00:24:23,200 --> 00:24:25,000
