439
00:26:25,700 --> 00:26:26,700
Suffering?

440
00:26:26,700 --> 00:26:28,600
What suffering?

441
00:26:29,600 --> 00:26:31,700
People who know shit

442
00:26:31,700 --> 00:26:34,600
